{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164390/extras/ui_border.png?t=1732140572\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164390/extras/aboutGifTop.gif?t=1732140572\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164390/extras/ui_border.png?t=1732140572\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have arrived at Sarpedon, a surreal island at the edge of the known world. Armed only with a bag, a sword, and your wits, you must continue your task as given:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">REACH THE ISLAND</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SLAY THE BEAST</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">RETURN WITH HER HEAD</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While the island may be cloaked in an isolating fog, you certainly aren't alone. The colorful cast of characters scattered around the island anticipate your arrival, some more anxiously than others. What will they be to you, friend or foe? What will you be to them? Explore the island, discover its inhabitants, and craft your story in Sarpedon, a solo dev's love letter to his favorite myth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A hand-crafted, open-world island environment to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique interactions with 5+ mythical characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 400+ lines of handwritten dialogue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Replayable mini-games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discussion of grief, remorse, and the ways in which we cope</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164390/extras/ui_border.png?t=1732140572\" /></p